        <Parent_String>clapper bells [300041874], suspended bells [300195496], bells (idiophones) [300041872], bells and sets of bells [300207481], percussion idiophones: hollow-bodied [300209185], percussion idiophones [300195371], directly struck idiophones [300041659], struck idiophones [300041657], idiophones [300041646], sound devices by acoustical characteristics [300041621], sound devices (equipment) [300387677], Sound Devices (hierarchy name) [300041619], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
